Sept 18 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Thursday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

NOMURA HOLDINGS INC <8604.T>  The Japan-based company named Kartadjaja Intan as its new head of investment banking in Indonesia, according to an internal memo seen by Reuters on Thursday. [ID:nL3N0RJ2OC]  SOCIETE GENERALE CORPORATE & INVESTMENT BANKING  The unit of Societe Generale <SOGN.PA> boosted its natural resources and energy financing team, naming senior executives in its Paris and Hong Kong offices.[ID:nL3N0RJ3LF]  SALAMANCA GROUP HOLDINGS LTD